{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-page-press-release-tsx","path":"/ar/media-center/doha-debates-hosts-ted-salon-'up-for-debate'-in-partnership-with-ted-and","result":{"data":{"contentfulPagePressRelease":{"id":"34b2b68f-283d-53e5-9985-7e08a100d471","slug":"doha-debates-hosts-ted-salon-'up-for-debate'-in-partnership-with-ted-and","title":"مناظرات الدوحة تستضيف صالون تيد \"استعدادًا للنقاش\" مع شركائها تيد وشيرد ستوديو","date":"2019-02-10","filterTags":null,"filterEntity":null,"heroImage":null,"modulesWrapper":[{"modules":[{"__typename":"ContentfulModuleBodyText","id":"c123078e-4fb9-5d70-89b1-fe5fc66cf1e7","text":{"childMarkdownRemark":{"html":"<p>استضافت \"مناظرات الدوحة\"، مبادرة من مبادرات مؤسسة قطر، سلسلة من المناقشات بالتعاون مع \"تيد\"، وذلك خلال صالون \"تيد\"، الذي نُظم بعنوان \"استعدادًا للنقاش\" في مدينة نيويورك الأمريكية.</p>"}}},{"__typename":"ContentfulModuleImageGallery","id":"68bb36d1-bbcb-5697-8f5c-89e0c0487f01","images":[{"caption":null,"image":{"id":"f33cfd62-f5ae-5d39-9c3a-4c3787112250","title":"Doha Debates TED Salon - Image 3","file":{"details":{"image":{"width":1024,"height":683}}},"sizes":{"aspectRatio":1.8666666666666667,"src":"//images.ctfassets.net/2h1qowfuxkq7/8KzOaIcxeOPHeHDUEtIFp/1e48375a3eb30ee6c72719d1353092c6/Doha_Debates_TED_Salon_-_Image_3.jpeg?w=1120&h=600&q=85","srcSet":"//images.ctfassets.net/2h1qowfuxkq7/8KzOaIcxeOPHeHDUEtIFp/1e48375a3eb30ee6c72719d1353092c6/Doha_Debates_TED_Salon_-_Image_3.jpeg?w=280&h=150&q=85 280w,\n//images.ctfassets.net/2h1qowfuxkq7/8KzOaIcxeOPHeHDUEtIFp/1e48375a3eb30ee6c72719d1353092c6/Doha_Debates_TED_Salon_-_Image_3.jpeg?w=560&h=300&q=85 560w,\n//images.ctfassets.net/2h1qowfuxkq7/8KzOaIcxeOPHeHDUEtIFp/1e48375a3eb30ee6c72719d1353092c6/Doha_Debates_TED_Salon_-_Image_3.jpeg?w=1024&h=549&q=85 1024w","srcWebp":"//images.ctfassets.net/2h1qowfuxkq7/8KzOaIcxeOPHeHDUEtIFp/1e48375a3eb30ee6c72719d1353092c6/Doha_Debates_TED_Salon_-_Image_3.jpeg?w=1120&h=600&q=85&fm=webp","srcSetWebp":"//images.ctfassets.